name: Shiny Chatot
description:
Chatot is a Normal/Flying-type parrot Pokémon from the Generation IV Pokémon games (Pokémon Diamond/Pearl). This Chatot has a rare Shiny color, with pink wings instead of the usual blue.

This art was drawn by Chatot Dungeon, a spinoff group from the Twitch channel Twitch Plays Pokémon that formed in 2014 after getting timed out in chat for saying "I like Chatot". The Chatot was later turned Shiny by French Pokémon YouTuber (PokéTuber) Sneaze, whose mascot is a Shiny Chatot named Mastouffe.
